01:12.202 --> 01:14.204
Prepare for docking!

01:15.466 --> 01:16.859
In position!

01:18.948 --> 01:20.210
Easy!

01:28.871 --> 01:30.742
Gate secure!

01:49.283 --> 01:51.154
Prisoner walking!

02:17.572 --> 02:19.965
Oh, great.
Another cellmate.

02:21.010 --> 02:22.533
No offense, pal.
You seem lovely.

02:23.969 --> 02:26.668
Uh...
Let'’s show you around.
Get you situated here.

02:26.842 --> 02:31.238
