02:52.302 --> 02:53.651
Sure thing. Have at it.

02:54.261 --> 02:56.350
Little shy, eh?

02:56.524 --> 02:59.701
I'’m not so bad once
you get to know me.

02:59.875 --> 03:01.137
Mmm.

03:01.790 --> 03:03.574
Don'’t be like that.

03:04.445 --> 03:07.012
We could be very happy to--

03:13.367 --> 03:16.370
I think I'’m gonna
do this without fingers
