03:20.156 --> 03:23.028
♪ Not fortune found
Nor fate divine♪

03:23.203 --> 03:26.597
♪ Come close to toping
The juice of the vine♪

03:26.771 --> 03:28.947
♪ With cherry crew
We sip and sway♪

03:29.121 --> 03:31.559
♪ Let'’s tip the tankard
