03:58.499 --> 04:00.762
By authority
of the Lords'’ Alliance,

04:00.936 --> 04:04.505
this Absolution Council
will now come to order

04:04.679 --> 04:09.684
in the case of Edgin Darvis
and Holga Kilgore.

04:10.946 --> 04:14.254
This is the second year of
incarceration for the crimes

04:14.428 --> 04:17.866
of grand larceny
and skullduggery.

04:18.040 --> 04:23.175
It is the task of this council
to determine your eligibility
for pardon.

04:23.350 --> 04:25.047
What say you?

04:25.221 --> 04:28.529
Thank you, Chancellor Anderton,
esteemed members of the council.

04:30.095 --> 04:34.404
Before I begin, I notice
that Chancellor Jarnathan
is not present.

04:34.578 --> 04:36.188
Should we perhaps wait?

04:36.363 --> 04:39.627
Chancellor Jarnathan was delayed
by the storm. You may begin.

04:39.801 --> 04:41.368
I see. It'’s just that I--

04:41.542 --> 04:44.849
we were really counting
on him to attend.

04:45.023 --> 04:47.199
Begin or waive
your statement.

04:47.374 --> 04:48.853
Very well.

04:50.681 --> 04:53.510
I should start
by giving you some context.

04:54.816 --> 04:57.079
You may be surprised to learn
I wasn'’t always a thief.

04:57.253 --> 05:01.126
Years ago, I became a member
of the Harpers faction,

05:01.301 --> 05:04.129
a network of spies who
swear an oath to fight tyranny,

05:04.304 --> 05:07.655
defend the oppressed
and to ask nothing in return.

05:07.829 --> 05:11.659
My wife, Zia,
