05:42.907 --> 05:45.649
"You don'’t have
to give us everything,
you only have to give us you."

05:45.823 --> 05:46.911
So what'’s the latest
on Jarnathan?

05:47.085 --> 05:49.000
Is he close by?
Because I can wait.

05:49.174 --> 05:51.263
Did you not hear what we said?Right, the storm.

05:51.438 --> 05:53.614
It'’s just that based on
what I know about Jarnathan,

05:53.788 --> 05:55.790
I think he'’d be especially
receptive to my story.

05:55.964 --> 05:57.966
And I'’d hate to have to wait
a whole other year

05:58.140 --> 06:00.229
