07:28.448 --> 07:32.147
I'’m sorry, it'’s just hard
to relive this...

07:33.583 --> 07:36.194
-without Jarnathan here.
-Again with this?

07:36.368 --> 07:38.370
But he missed the most
important part of my backstory!

07:38.545 --> 07:40.677
How can he judge me
without knowing my motivation?

07:40.851 --> 07:44.376
We are entirely capable
of deciding your case
without Jarnathan.

07:44.551 --> 07:47.205
-Get on with it!
-Fine. Where was I? Uh...

07:47.379 --> 07:50.731
By night, I'’d come home
to my loving wife,
and daughter Kira.

07:50.905 --> 07:52.559
You went back too far.
Stop stalling!

07:52.733 --> 07:55.213
Right, sorry.
Yeah, broad strokes.

07:55.387 --> 08:00.218
The next few months
were among my most shameful.

08:02.917 --> 08:04.309
That'’s when I met Holga.

08:05.006 --> 08:06.224
She took pity on me.

08:07.487 --> 08:09.967
Well,
she took pity on the baby.

08:10.141 --> 08:12.709
Holga was a fellow resident
