08:13.928 --> 08:16.583
Many years before, she'’d
been cast out of her tribe

08:16.757 --> 08:18.410
for falling in love
with an outsider.

08:22.676 --> 08:25.461
We quickly became like
brother and sister.

08:25.635 --> 08:29.073
With a relationship built
on trust and mutual respect.

08:32.424 --> 08:35.079
Neither of us had money
or an honest way to earn it,

08:35.253 --> 08:39.127
