10:30.499 --> 10:33.415
Not yet.
But this is the last one.

10:34.329 --> 10:35.635
Trust me.

10:40.596 --> 10:42.467
Chin up, Bug.
We'’ll be right back.

10:42.642 --> 10:44.252
I didn'’t tell her
