10:46.210 --> 10:47.821
And, well,

10:48.430 --> 10:49.953
to shit it went.

11:20.723 --> 11:21.724
See you soon, love.

11:33.780 --> 11:35.129
Intruders!

11:35.825 --> 11:36.739
There they are!

11:42.310 --> 11:43.964
We don'’t hurt anyone.

12:00.154 --> 12:02.678
She'’s caught in the Time Stop!
