me to another two years,

12:38.235 --> 12:40.716
or 20 for that matter,

12:40.890 --> 12:45.721
it would never be punishment
enough for the worst crime
I ever committed...

12:47.549 --> 12:49.899
robbing my daughter
of her father.

12:50.073 --> 12:53.685
But know that,
if you do choose to free me,

12:53.860 --> 12:56.950
I'’ll spend the rest of my days
trying to right that wrong.

12:58.299 --> 12:59.953
