13:14.054 --> 13:15.664
Jarnathan!Pardon my belatedness.

13:15.838 --> 13:18.362
I can'’t tell you how happy
I am to see you!Step away!

13:18.536 --> 13:21.104
Holga, now!Guards!

13:21.278 --> 13:23.106
Release me, sir!

13:23.280 --> 13:25.282
She'’s throwing potatoes!

13:26.109 --> 13:27.328
Oh, Jarnathan!

13:29.330 --> 13:30.853
