17:59.426 --> 18:00.427
Dad.

18:01.384 --> 18:02.603
Holga?

18:03.212 --> 18:04.213
Kira.

18:08.130 --> 18:09.479
Oh!

18:09.653 --> 18:12.308
-I missed you so much.
-Hello, Bug.

