20:08.032 --> 20:09.817
Good behavior.Yeah, behaving good.

20:09.991 --> 20:11.819
Ah. I see.

20:11.993 --> 20:14.213
Well, welcome. Welcome back.

20:15.388 --> 20:17.520
Oh, that'’s blistering.
