I do apologize.
It'’s scorching hot.

21:17.406 --> 21:19.234
Um, Sofina.

21:20.670 --> 21:22.672
Would you mind very much, um...

21:23.325 --> 21:24.587
Certainly.

21:28.939 --> 21:29.897
Hmm.

21:30.071 --> 21:32.291
Good. Thank you. I-- I'’m...

21:32.465 --> 21:36.033
I didn'’t realize you were
