is my arm.

1:05:31.362 --> 1:05:34.104
How could he hear that?I hear that as well.

1:05:34.931 --> 1:05:35.932
I hate you.

1:05:50.120 --> 1:05:52.296
The path to the ruins
is just here.

1:06:00.695 --> 1:06:01.609
Keep still!

1:06:05.309 --> 1:06:06.614
Rochnon.

1:06:06.788 --> 1:06:09.617
Intellect devourers.
Small but formidable.

1:06:09.791 --> 1:06:13.534
They stun their targets
and consume the brain,
taking control of the body.

1:06:13.708 --> 1:06:15.667
What do we do?Make no sound.

1:06:16.798 --> 1:06:18.975
They'’re drawn to mental energy.

1:06:19.149 --> 1:06:23.457
The higher the intelligence
of the prey, the more likely
