1:06:40.561 --> 1:06:42.346
Well, that'’s a little hurtful.

1:06:43.651 --> 1:06:47.307
There it is.
The Hanging City of Dolblunde.

1:06:48.526 --> 1:06:52.356
The helmet lies on the far side
of this chasm.

1:06:52.530 --> 1:06:56.882
But be warned,
the bridge is protected
by an ancient Gnomish trap.

1:06:57.056 --> 1:07:00.277
There is a precise formula
we must follow so as not to
trigger the mechanism.

1:07:00.451 --> 1:07:03.280
What'’s the formula?It'’s quite simple.

1:07:03.454 --> 1:07:05.891
Starting from the center,
use odd-numbered blocks only,

1:07:06.065 --> 1:07:08.328
moving forward with each step,
except for every fifth step,

1:07:08.502 --> 1:07:09.634
which must be a lateral move.

1:07:09.808 --> 1:07:11.462
Left or right, it matters not,

1:07:11.636 --> 1:07:13.594
so long as the leader
and the laggard
remain equidistant.

1:07:13.768 --> 1:07:16.771
After which, proceed.
Again, odd-numbered blocks only.

1:07:16.945 --> 1:07:20.036
However, at the midpoint
we switch
to even-numbered blocks.

1:07:20.210 --> 1:07:22.908
Same pattern,
except now a lateral move
after the fourth step,

1:07:23.082 --> 1:07:25.258
until we reach the three--

1:07:33.527 --> 1:07:35.181
I--

1:07:35.355 --> 1:07:37.140
I may have...

1:07:37.314 --> 1:07:39.446
put my foot
on the bridge.

1:07:39.620 --> 1:07:41.927
Didn'’t realize that'’s where
it technically started.

1:07:44.669 --> 1:07:47.019
So... sorry.

1:07:52.720 --> 1:07:55.071
It'’s not very
structurally sound.

1:07:56.942 --> 1:07:59.858
Can'’t you just magic us across?

1:08:00.032 --> 1:08:02.817
It'’s too far for telekinesis.

1:08:02.991 --> 1:08:05.603
I'’ve got some rope in my bag.

1:08:05.777 --> 1:08:07.344
I could tie it to the axe.

1:08:07.518 --> 1:08:09.694
Toss it across
so it sticks to the rock.

1:08:09.868 --> 1:08:13.263
You know rocks are hard, right?Shut up.

1:08:13.437 --> 1:08:14.742
Where did you get that?

1:08:16.179 --> 1:08:17.571
What,
Marlamin'’s walking stick?

1:08:17.745 --> 1:08:19.965
I swiped it from a wizard
over in the Greypeaks.

1:08:20.139 --> 1:08:21.967
That'’s not a walking stick.

1:08:23.621 --> 1:08:25.188
It'’s a Hither-Thither staff.

1:08:25.362 --> 1:08:28.191
A what?Should have a range
of around 500 yards.

1:08:29.670 --> 1:08:30.802
Watch.

1:08:30.976 --> 1:08:32.108
Hither.

1:08:33.283 --> 1:08:34.284
Thither.

1:08:36.329 --> 1:08:38.853
It works!

1:08:41.334 --> 1:08:42.553
See?

1:08:43.554 --> 1:08:45.643
Didn'’t even need the bridge!

1:08:46.557 --> 1:08:47.862
I did good.

1:08:49.125 --> 1:08:50.213
Good save.

1:09:30.818 --> 1:09:35.693
This I give you now,
trusting that you will
protect it with your very life.

1:09:36.389 --> 1:09:37.521
I will.

1:09:39.000 --> 1:09:40.350
Hold this.

1:09:45.006 --> 1:09:46.878
There is evil here.

1:09:58.977 --> 1:10:00.108
Are those...

1:10:00.935 --> 1:10:02.241
Thayan assassins.

1:10:02.415 --> 1:10:05.505
