Why? You killed them all.

1:12:03.101 --> 1:12:05.712
'’Tis no simple feat
to kill that
which is already dead.

1:12:10.717 --> 1:12:12.850
Ready for
the next bout, Yendar?

1:12:15.156 --> 1:12:16.810
Quickly!

1:13:04.945 --> 1:13:06.817
That'’s one pudgy dragon.

1:13:06.991 --> 1:13:10.168
It'’s Themberchaud.
He must have found a new den.

1:13:10.342 --> 1:13:11.822
Did he eat the last one?

1:14:29.116 --> 1:14:30.204
I got you!

1:14:41.346 --> 1:14:43.174
It'’s a dead end!

1:14:43.957 --> 1:14:45.829
Simon! Up there!

1:15:38.011 --> 1:15:39.230
Thanks for that.

1:15:40.187 --> 1:15:41.972
You'’d have done
the same for me.

1:15:43.713 --> 1:15:44.714
Yeah.

1:15:47.281 --> 1:15:48.848
