1:15:59.598 --> 1:16:01.644
Come on! He'’s stuck!

1:16:03.080 --> 1:16:03.994
So are we.

1:16:10.435 --> 1:16:12.263
We'’re gonna drown!

1:16:12.437 --> 1:16:15.527
