you did in Triboar?

1:16:23.753 --> 1:16:24.710
Fresh-cut grass smell?

1:16:24.884 --> 1:16:27.191
No, the flame finger one.

1:16:27.365 --> 1:16:29.106
Yeah, why?Holga, hit him!

1:16:29.280 --> 1:16:31.108
You want to make him angrier?

1:16:31.282 --> 1:16:33.676
When I say so,
everybody goes underwater.

1:16:33.850 --> 1:16:36.287
And that'’ll be your cue, Simon,
all right?

1:16:36.461 --> 1:16:38.071
What are you looking at?

1:16:38.245 --> 1:16:41.074
A Harper shaking off
his slumber.

1:16:42.598 --> 1:16:43.599
Go, Holga!

1:16:48.342 --> 1:16:49.517
Again!

1:16:52.738 --> 1:16:53.565
Now!

1:17:32.517 --> 1:17:33.953
This is where I leave you.

1:17:34.127 --> 1:17:36.303
I wish you every success
on your journey.

1:17:38.479 --> 1:17:40.438
You'’re not coming?Would that I could.

1:17:40.612 --> 1:17:43.049
But this is your quest.

1:17:43.223 --> 1:17:46.574
