isn'’t great.

1:17:56.672 --> 1:17:57.760
Mmm.

1:17:59.457 --> 1:18:02.765
In those instances where
faith wanes and doubt waxes,

1:18:02.939 --> 1:18:04.418
I recall
the Tenets of the Ancients...

1:18:04.592 --> 1:18:06.333
Okay. See you later.

1:18:21.914 --> 1:18:23.263
There he goes.

1:18:25.483 --> 1:18:27.093
Just wandering off.

1:18:28.616 --> 1:18:30.967
