1:18:32.142 --> 1:18:34.057
Uh-oh. Wait a minute.
He'’s coming up on a rock.

1:18:34.231 --> 1:18:36.407
Is he gonna go around?

1:18:36.581 --> 1:18:37.843
Nope.

1:18:38.017 --> 1:18:39.845
Right over the rock.

1:18:47.113 --> 1:18:48.854
