rests on you.

1:19:05.044 --> 1:19:07.133
Come on.

1:19:30.113 --> 1:19:33.507
There he is,
the great Simon Aumar.

1:19:33.681 --> 1:19:36.597
Sorcerer descended
from wizarding blood.

1:19:36.772 --> 1:19:38.034
Who are you?

1:19:38.686 --> 1:19:40.166
Don'’t you know me?

1:19:41.820 --> 1:19:43.909
