the helmet flew off
the second you put it on.

1:20:44.013 --> 1:20:45.841
Well, time moves
differently there.

1:20:46.015 --> 1:20:47.843
Okay,
I'’ll try a different approach.

1:20:48.017 --> 1:20:50.019
Great. New approach. Try it.

1:20:51.629 --> 1:20:52.760
You got this.
You got this.

1:20:59.289 --> 1:21:01.465
You'’re getting better.
You didn'’t fly as far.

1:21:01.639 --> 1:21:03.032
Stick with it.

1:21:03.206 --> 1:21:04.772
We have six hours till
we leave for Neverwinter.

1:21:04.947 --> 1:21:06.818
You fail, I never
get my family back.

1:21:06.992 --> 1:21:08.080
Brilliant.

1:21:27.273 --> 1:21:29.449
I'’ve never seen
a bigger coward.

1:21:29.623 --> 1:21:32.061
Coward?
You'’re under here, too.

1:21:32.713 --> 1:21:33.932
Fine. I'’ll handle it.

1:21:34.106 --> 1:21:35.891
No, no, no.

1:21:37.240 --> 1:21:38.545
I'’ve got this.

1:21:40.852 --> 1:21:43.159
And you want
to be a Harper.

1:21:43.333 --> 1:21:44.595
Quiet!

1:21:48.991 --> 1:21:51.167
Oh, God. Damn.

1:21:51.776 --> 1:21:53.082
There it is.

1:21:54.605 --> 1:21:56.694
Stop trying to capture it.

1:22:00.916 --> 1:22:02.613
You just have to let it go.

1:22:04.049 --> 1:22:05.137
Ed!

1:22:06.138 --> 1:22:08.575
Ed! We'’ve got a problem.

1:22:08.749 --> 1:22:10.142
I can'’t do it.

1:22:11.187 --> 1:22:12.971
-The helmet?
-I'’ve been at it for hours!

1:22:13.145 --> 1:22:14.930
I can'’t get past
