1:22:23.895 --> 1:22:27.116
Oh. yeah, okay. Yeah.
Thanks, Holga. I'’ll just do it.

1:22:27.290 --> 1:22:30.075
This is exactly what I told you
would happen back at the tavern,

1:22:30.249 --> 1:22:33.078
